	<h1 class="title">时尚制造业全球污染第二强，仅次于石油行业</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/49585/small/49585.jpg?1422286480" alt="">
